# Cursor AI Rules for Phyllux Superrepo

## CRITICAL: DO NOT MODIFY

Under NO circumstances should AI modify these:
- LICENSE files (in any repo)
- PRIOR_ART.md, PATENTS.md, DISCLOSURE.md files
- INVENTORSHIP_DECLARATION.md
- TIMESTAMP.md
- Maturity tags in phyllux-inventions-wip
- Commit history or git tags
- Any file in legal/ directories

## Qualified Language Requirements

ALWAYS use qualified language:
- "may provide"
- "designed to"
- "simulations suggest"
- "could enable"
- "appears to"

NEVER use absolute claims:
- "guarantees"
- "proven"
- "definitely"
- Absolute performance assertions

## Repository Modification Rules

### biomimetic-inventions-public
- ❌ Do NOT modify source code
- ❌ Do NOT change dates or version numbers
- ❌ Do NOT alter technical figures
- ✅ Can reference via URLs

### phyllux-framework
- ❌ Do NOT change licensing terms
- ❌ Do NOT modify templates
- ❌ Do NOT alter PHYLUX_SPINE.md
- ✅ Can reference framework

### phyllux-inventions-wip
- ❌ Do NOT change fusion content
- ❌ Do NOT modify maturity tags
- ❌ Do NOT delete fusion directories
- ✅ Can reference fusions

### phyllux-superrepo
- ✅ Can update CONTROL_PANEL.md
- ✅ Can add pipeline entries
- ✅ Can generate briefs
- ✅ Can run analytics scripts
- ❌ Do NOT modify .cursor/rules
- ❌ Do NOT change REVENUE_MODEL.md tier definitions

## Safe Modification Zones

Safe to modify in superrepo:
- CONTROL_PANEL.md (daily updates)
- partnerships/pipeline/ (deal tracking)
- OPPORTUNITY_MATRIX.md (scoring updates)
- Partner briefs (using templates)
- Analytics script outputs

Never modify:
- LICENSE, PRIOR_ART, PATENTS, DISCLOSURE files
- Maturity tags
- Commit history
- Legal files

## Read-Only Principle

This superrepo NEVER modifies the three existing repos:
- biomimetic-inventions-public
- phyllux-framework
- phyllux-inventions-wip

All references via URLs or read-only data access.

## Prior Art Protection

- All repos reference prior art dates consistently
- No modifications to LICENSE, PRIOR_ART, PATENTS, DISCLOSURE files
- Defensive publication strategy maintained
